{"tid":2089751,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"臨時「二哥」劉業成與屋企人篤灰單野係有關","createTime":"2020-07-01T22:47:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T15:49:14.000Z","uid":26770,"like":57,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"db9666fa386be95443d3009b8a92f4c523e73a71","tid":2089751,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T22:47:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2089743/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2089743/page/1</a><br />\n我隨便估都可以估到可能係空姐/父母太驚同親戚商量比藍絲親人出賣<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n做情報最撚ON9係公開情報源, 香港警魔SPIN去父母篤100%唔係</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>而呢招故意揚開分化反抗者就係納納粹警魔劉業成的招式</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n記唔記得劉業成獲委任臨時「二哥」後<br />\n示威現場無暴露的便衣故意係記者面前同防暴相認上狗車走</span>"},{"pid":"4597ce0bc761082d0a6a973ed4458dfd444bedd8","tid":2089751,"uid":24730,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T23:00:47.000Z","msg":"可能班狗喺支共協助下用法庭及私隱條例唔容許嘅手段追縱到義士，所以故意嫁禍畀佢家人，以掩飾佢哋嘅非法手段。"},{"pid":"2cde644ee402f1a8c844cd29f759088d0dca93f3","tid":2089751,"uid":26770,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T23:08:08.000Z","msg":"呢招根本係香港納粹警魔想引誘人去攻擊手足父母<br />\n劉業成條死仆街做開呢科野<br />\n<br />\n就算無人上當<br />\n<ins>我覺得警一哥會搵自己手下的元朗黑幫扮示威者去打手足父母</ins><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能用大陸海康CAM的後門程式做"},{"pid":"8961bf360fa6f4bcb44e2330ac65ee6143674cfe","tid":2089751,"uid":1072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T23:11:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"12d4824cf9f52f1a9a5450d0e2101f1c379319b8","tid":2089751,"uid":318628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T23:14:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\